## Project profile

- **Type:** Static HTML/CSS/JS marketing site
- **Version source:** `downloads/releases.js` → `window.CYB_RELEASES.version`
- **Build output:** `dist_web/` (gitignored — FTP upload only)
- **Deploy target:** Freehostia `public_html/` + Cloudflare cache purge
- **Production:** https://checkyourbackup.com/

