## hola — project extras

After global hola steps, verify paths exist:

`index.html`, `robots.txt`, `sitemap.xml`, `.htaccess`, `assets/`, `blog/`, `docs/`,
`downloads/releases.js`, `scripts/build_dist_web.sh`, `scripts/build_dist_web.bat`

Dev server:

```bash
python3 -m http.server 5173
```

Verify: `curl -s -o /dev/null -w "%{http_code}" http://localhost:5173/` → `200`

Warn if `instagram/captures/` is missing PNGs on `main` (check unmerged branches).

